---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About | Dark Matter Trading" description="Learn about Dark Matter Trading — a proprietary quantitative research firm trading renewable energy on European markets.">
  <section class="page-hero">
    <span class="page-label mono">ABOUT // COMPANY</span>
    <h1>Trading the<br />Energy Transition.</h1>
    <p>
      Dark Matter Trading is a proprietary quantitative trading firm
      headquartered in Sofia, Bulgaria. We specialize in algorithmic
      high-frequency trading on renewable energy markets — specifically solar
      and wind energy on the Independent Bulgarian Energy Exchange (IBEX).
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="about-grid">
    <div class="about-block">
      <h3>What We Do</h3>
      <p>
        We build and operate fully automated trading systems that provide
        liquidity to European energy markets. Our algorithms process real-time
        weather data, grid telemetry, and market microstructure to execute
        trades at speeds and precision impossible for human operators.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="about-block">
      <h3>Our Market</h3>
      <p>
        The Bulgarian energy market is at the frontier of Europe's renewable
        transition. Solar and wind generation create systematic volatility that
        our quantitative models are designed to capture. We are active
        participants on IBEX, trading day-ahead and intraday products.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="about-block">
      <h3>Our Edge</h3>
      <p>
        Traditional energy traders rely on delayed macro-level forecasts. We
        operate at a fundamentally different level — combining proprietary
        atmospheric models, direct grid-state analysis, and machine learning to
        price energy before the broader market reacts.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="about-block">
      <h3>Expansion</h3>
      <p>
        While IBEX remains our core market, we are actively developing
        infrastructure to expand across the European Synchronous Grid. Adjacent
        markets with growing renewable penetration present natural opportunities
        for our technology and approach.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="principles-section">
    <div class="principles-header">
      <h2>Operating Principles.</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="principles-list">
      <div class="principle">
        <span class="principle-num mono">01</span>
        <div>
          <h4>Proprietary Capital Only</h4>
          <p>We trade exclusively with our own capital. No outside funds, no retail clients, no conflicts of interest.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="principle">
        <span class="principle-num mono">02</span>
        <div>
          <h4>Research-Driven</h4>
          <p>Every trading decision originates from quantitative research. We do not employ discretionary traders.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="principle">
        <span class="principle-num mono">03</span>
        <div>
          <h4>Technology-First</h4>
          <p>Infrastructure is not a support function — it is the product. Our systems are engineered for reliability, speed, and adaptability.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-hero {
    padding: 8rem 0 6rem 0;
    max-width: 900px;
  }

  .page-label {
    color: var(--cherenkov);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .page-hero h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4.5rem);
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .page-hero p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--slate);
    max-width: 700px;
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 3rem;
    padding: 6rem 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .about-block h3 {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
  }

  .about-block p {
    color: var(--slate);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .principles-section {
    padding: 6rem 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .principles-header h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .principles-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2.5rem;
  }

  .principle {
    display: flex;
    gap: 2rem;
    align-items: flex-start;
    border-left: 1px solid var(--slate);
    padding-left: 2rem;
    transition: border-color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .principle:hover {
    border-left-color: var(--cherenkov);
  }

  .principle-num {
    color: var(--cherenkov);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .principle h4 {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .principle p {
    color: var(--slate);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .page-hero {
      padding: 5rem 0 4rem 0;
    }

    .about-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2.5rem;
    }

    .principle {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>
